//- "layout" has "content" and "sidebar" blocks that should be defined here
block content
  - if (!currentSessionUser.id)
    p Welcome to #{title}.
    p Log in or create an account to see your contaggs.
  - else
    p Greetings #{ currentSessionUser.name }


block sidebar
